(area_cell_area, area_cell_area).explanation: A variable cannot have a causal relationship with itself as it represents the same measurement;

(area_cell_area, time).explanation: Cell area and execution time are independent design metrics that do not directly cause changes in each other;

(area_cell_area, area_net_area).explanation: These represent different physical area components in chip design that are independently determined and do not directly cause changes in each other;
